[[Classes]]: [[Classes:Demon|Demon]]&rarr;<u>StealthDemon</u>


A [[stealth monster|stealth]] version of the demon, not to be confused with a {{Class|spectre}}: the Spectre is always "[[fuzz]]y", but the stealth demon is totally invisible except when attacking or taking damage.
==== [[ZScript]] definition ====
{{ZScriptDefinitionNote|actors/doom/stealthmonsters.zs}}
 class StealthDemon : Demon
 {
 	Default
 	{
 		+{{Flag|STEALTH}}
 		{{Property|RenderStyle}} "Translucent";
 		{{Property|Alpha}} 0;
 		{{Property|Obituary}} "$OB_STEALTHDEMON";
 		{{Property|HitObituary}} "$OB_STEALTHDEMON";
 	}
 }
